{"tid":1846901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"死得有價值嘅叫犧牲","createTime":"2020-01-27T19:10:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T19:14:36.000Z","uid":200545,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ebe04b67db67c4f48add7deb7ce1f6a947ddf0cf","tid":1846901,"uid":200545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:10:16.000Z","msg":"死得冇價值嘅叫送頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n一日未封關<br />\n都代表著有無數個嘅肺炎病人要你去救<br />\n用條命作賭注去救一班支那狗值得嗎？<br />\n萬一真係不幸瀨咗嘢<br />\n下一個人又頂上<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不停loop<br />\n你諗下你地醫護人手多家係支那狗多？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n為咗班支那狗死值得嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔想白白送頭比班支那狗同港共嘅<br />\n記住一定要罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n辛苦曬你地 係時候要休息下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ab55bed1a1e2906caa4d2e1aecbe589c460e4be","tid":1846901,"uid":38563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:11:44.000Z","msg":"醫護罷工就勢在必行<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n題外話：<br />\n<br />\n黎明行動送頭<br />\n港島遊行集會送頭<br />\n深夜整連儂牆送頭<br />\n派傳單都會畀藍絲割肚不了<br />\n<br />\n而家我哋打旗號叫政府封關阻肺炎呀<br />\n民建聯都唔會夠膽出聲反對啦 粉嶺單野政府都hea應啦<br />\n<br />\n另外想問工會過咗咁多個月有幾多人入咗會？<br />\n全民大三罷？<br />\n唔好話無限期啦 就算一日 短期內我都睇唔出我哋有咩條件做得到 到時幾多生化人入咗關？再搞無限期三罷已經遲<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">因為到時已經有唔少香港人奶咗野 咁醫護仲點罷工呀</span><br />\n<br />\n醒下啦送頭<br />\n你話畀我知唔送頭仲可以點"},{"pid":"ffac63470e2f0fef4e6cb8a6bc558c5ec9c211d8","tid":1846901,"uid":27993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:12:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SuZNqit.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSuZNqit.jpg&h=3a2c53be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n關都未封 就想你地送死呀<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">港共德政 停止來往武漢高鐵及航班</span><br />\n咩話? 武漢一早封左市 你唔封佢都黎唔到 咁叫做左野?<br />\n依加叫你封關呀 唔俾支那人入呀撚屌!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭: </span>你射咗啦? 咁我幫你戴返個套先<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">港共德政更新 24小時火化服務</span><br />\n所有預防措施都不了 病了火化就可以<br />\n仲可以連埋黑警囤積已久嘅無可疑屍體一齊火化<br />\n林鄭等咗好耐架啦 掟落樓都慳返<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林: 不如戴返個套<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭:</span> 你射啦！我搵咗醫院24小時墮胎啦"},{"pid":"41880ebb9fa775f54dbae01126682d11897632ca","tid":1846901,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:12:35.000Z","msg":"True"},{"pid":"70ac0d98bb700278762dfaf629ac91edbbd1656c","tid":1846901,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:14:16.000Z","msg":"罷工有咩做？不如包圍政府相關設施！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1846866\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1846866</a>"},{"pid":"2fc0f6c05bdd76c1e0479ba35f8151b1ab31b2c4","tid":1846901,"uid":310461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:14:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9sX9FSQTOy8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9sX9FSQTOy8&d=gjA94EiKSJsk9JMrtOnM5pKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=26f1cd20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9sX9FSQTOy8</a>"}]}